  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下零售系统的数据流向。核心是Retail_CouponSystem和Retail_Inventory这两个模块，先画个流程图吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，CouponSystem这边我注意到需要区分不同的功能节点。您说的Audit、Barg、Code这三个都是CouponSystem下的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Audit是审计模块，Barg是议价处理，Code是优惠码管理，都属于CouponSystem。Inventory那边有Define和Bail两个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先画出这五个节点：Audit、Barg、Code、Define、Bail。另外还需要Place和Signal、Risk这些中间状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Signal",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。Risk是上游风险信号，触发Signal状态，然后Signal会驱动Barg进行议价响应。Place是库存位置，通过Press操作触发后续流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Risk→Signal→Barg这条链加上了，还有Place--Press。现在处理CouponSystem内部的流向：Code应该指向Define对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Code优惠码验证后要同步到Inventory的Define节点做库存定义。另外Audit也要连到Define，审计结果影响库存策略。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Code→Define和Audit→Define。Define到Barg也有关系吧？库存定义会触发议价？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Define→Barg，库存定义变化会触发议价流程。还有Bail和Barg之间是双向的，库存释放和议价状态互相影响。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了Define→Barg和Barg↔Bail的双向关系。等等，Bail→Barg这个方向确认吗？还是只有Barg→Bail？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我重新理一下：Bail指向Barg，同时Barg也指向Bail，确实是双向。但Bail→Barg是库存释放触发议价，Barg→Bail是议价结果影响库存释放。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，保留双向箭头。所有节点检查一遍：Audit、Bail、Barg、Code、Define、Place、Risk、Signal，关系也都齐了。方向是LR横向布局对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Place",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，横向布局，从左到右体现数据流向：Risk和Place在左侧输入，经过Signal、Press等处理，到右侧的Barg和Bail形成闭环。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
